************** OLD VERSION ****************



What can I say ? It's the RPD of Resident Evil 2 (Biohazard 2).

CT start in the West part of the building, and Terro in the East part.

There are two bombsites, one in the main hall and one in the parking.

I used a lot of screeshots of the game to make this map.

Enjoy :)
